  `opinion_of_staff` mediumtext,
  `opinion_of_hrm` mediumtext,
  `eval_task` text CHARACTER SET latin1,

  `period_time_from` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `period_time_to` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `is_approved` tinyint(4) DEFAULT '0',
  `hrm_is_approved` tinyint(4) DEFAULT '0',
  `salary_increment_date` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_at` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_at` datetime DEFAULT NULL,

	INDEX `schedule` (`status`, `crawled_at`, `id`),
	INDEX `watchers` (`watchers`)
